OL,3,CCalls for 'Kiena's Law' to improve
OL,4,Crecognition of domestic abuse-related
OL,5,Csuicide
OL,7,FCampaigners are urging the government
OL,8,Fto introduce a law to make domestic
OL,9,Fabuse-related suicide a specific
OL,10,Fcriminal offence - in memory of a
OL,11,Fyoung mum.
OL,13,FKiena Dawes - a hairdresser from
OL,14,FLancashire - took her own life in July
OL,15,F2022 after being subject to prolonged
OL,16,Fdomestic abuse by her former partner
OL,17,FRyan Wellings.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1783702080
OL,3,CCalls for 'Kiena's Law' to improve
OL,4,Crecognition of domestic abuse-related
OL,5,Csuicide
OL,7,FWellings was found guilty of assault
OL,8,Fand prolonged domestic violence
OL,9,Ftowards his partner, but was cleared
OL,10,Fof her manslaughter after a six-week
OL,11,Ftrial at Preston Crown Court.
OL,13,FHe was the first defendant to face
OL,14,Ftrial for the unlawful killing of his
OL,15,Fpartner after her suicide following
OL,16,Fdomestic violence.
OL,18,FKiena's mum Angela previously
OL,19,Fdescribed Kiena as "a rare gem" who
OL,20,Fbrought "so much love and kindness to
OL,21,Fthis world".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1783702080
OL,3,CCalls for 'Kiena's Law' to improve
OL,4,Crecognition of domestic abuse-related
OL,5,Csuicide
OL,7,FShe said: "I honestly cannot put into
OL,8,Fwords how much it breaks my heart that
OL,9,Fher beautiful baby girl doesn't have a
OL,10,Fmummy here because of that monster."
OL,12,FPhylis Daly also lost her daughter
OL,13,FJessie Laverack, from Beverley, East
OL,14,FYorkshire, to domestic abuse-related
OL,15,Fsuicide in 2018.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
