FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1783702080
OL,3,CCalls for 'Kiena's Law' to improve
OL,4,Crecognition of domestic abuse-related
OL,5,Csuicide
OL,7,FAt an event held in Blackpool to
OL,8,Faddress growing concerns about the
OL,9,Flink between sustained domestic abuse
OL,10,Fand suicide, she said: "Jessie died
OL,11,Fbecause of domestic abuse. She wanted
OL,12,Fto live but she couldn't live that
OL,13,Flife of domestic abuse.
OL,15,F"People very simply see an injury or
OL,16,Fif there's some visual signs there but
OL,17,Fwhat people can't see is coercive
OL,18,Fcontrol is sometimes invisible or the
OL,19,Fstories that are secret because people
OL,20,Fare embarrassed."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1783702080
OL,3,CCalls for 'Kiena's Law' to improve
OL,4,Crecognition of domestic abuse-related
OL,5,Csuicide
OL,7,FCampaigners say current law does not
OL,8,Fconsistently recognise where prolonged
OL,9,Fabuse, including coercive and
OL,10,Fcontrolling behaviour, is a
OL,11,Fcontributing factor in a victim's
OL,12,Fdeath.
OL,14,FLancashire's Police and Crime
OL,15,FCommissioner Clive Grunshaw has
OL,16,Flaunched a petition called _KienasLaw.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1783702080
OL,3,CCalls for 'Kiena's Law' to improve
OL,4,Crecognition of domestic abuse-related
OL,5,Csuicide
OL,7,FHe said: "What we're looking for is a
OL,8,Fchange in legislation for a stand
OL,9,Falone offence for manslaughter around
OL,10,Fdomestic abuse-related suicide but
OL,11,Falso to look at how we can tweak
OL,12,Fexisting legislation so that coercive
OL,13,Fcontrol is recognised more by the
OL,14,Fcriminal justice system for the effect
OL,15,Fit has on victims."
OL,17,FThe event in Blackpool featured a
OL,18,F'Blue Shoes' exhibition in St John's
OL,19,FSquare, displaying 150 pairs of blue
OL,20,Fshoes - one for every life lost last
OL,21,Fyear to domestic abuse related suicide.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1783702080
OL,3,CCalls for 'Kiena's Law' to improve
OL,4,Crecognition of domestic abuse-related
OL,5,Csuicide
OL,7,FMr Grunshaw said: "When you listen to
OL,8,Fthe families of victims like Kiena,
OL,9,Fyou can't fail to be moved by the pain
OL,10,Fanguish and suffering and the sense of
OL,11,Finjustice they feel so they are fully
OL,12,Fbehind this campaign.
OL,14,F"They want justice for their loved one
OL,15,Fand they want justice so the law
OL,16,Frecognises what their loved one has
OL,17,Fbeen through."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1783702080
OL,3,CCalls for 'Kiena's Law' to improve
OL,4,Crecognition of domestic abuse-related
OL,5,Csuicide
OL,7,FMr Grunshaw confirmed the petition
OL,8,Falready has support from government
OL,9,Fministers and families of victims, but
OL,10,Fthere is no timeline on when change
OL,11,Fcould happen.
OL,13,FHe said: "The petition we have
OL,14,Flaunched in the name of Kiena is a way
OL,15,Fthat people can demonstrate their
OL,16,Fsupport of this campaign."
OL,18,FFrank Mullane is the CEO of Advocacy
OL,19,FAfter Fatal Domestic Abuse (AAFDA).
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1783702080
OL,3,CCalls for 'Kiena's Law' to improve
OL,4,Crecognition of domestic abuse-related
OL,5,Csuicide
OL,7,FHe said: "The courts are currently
OL,8,Fusing a law which does not work when
OL,9,Fthere is a suicide caused by domestic
OL,10,Fabuse.
OL,12,F"People perceive manslaughter very
OL,13,Foften as physical acts of violence.
OL,14,FThey struggle to think about it as
OL,15,Fsomeone taking their own life after
OL,16,Fhorrific domestic abuse over many
OL,17,Fyears which is homicide that's what
OL,18,Fwe're saying.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1783702080
OL,3,CCalls for 'Kiena's Law' to improve
OL,4,Crecognition of domestic abuse-related
OL,5,Csuicide
OL,7,F"That current law is complex for jurys
OL,8,Fto get their heads around. We are
OL,9,Fasking jurys to deal with very complex
OL,10,Fconcepts. The law needs to change to
OL,11,Frecognise the direct correction
OL,12,Fbetween domestic abuse and suicide.
OL,14,F"Domestic abuse causes suicide."
OL,16,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,17,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,18,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,19,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
